These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Game: snooker, chess, canasta, monopoly
1. Game:monopoly is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Game:chess##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Game:canasta is on the left or right of Game:monopoly##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Game        | snooker | chess   | monopoly | canasta    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: liverpool, berlin, boston, new-york
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. City:liverpool is on the left of City:boston##1
3. City:boston is in an odd position##4
4. City:liverpool == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. City:berlin is on the right of City:boston##1
6. City:liverpool == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | new-york    | liverpool | boston | berlin    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: baseball, biathlon, snowboarding, water-polo
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Sport:water-polo is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Sport:snowboarding is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Sport:biathlon##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:biathlon is on the right of Sport:snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | water-polo | snowboarding | biathlon    | baseball      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

