2. Beverage:lemonade is on the left of Beverage:tea##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | lemonade | tea | water | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

