.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
Hobby: singing, gardening, chess, skydiving
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Hobby:skydiving##1
2. Hobby:gardening == Music-Genre:punk##1
3. Hobby:chess is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:jazz is in an odd position##4
6. Hobby:singing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | chess | gardening |

