Pet: hamster, ferret, bird, goldfish
1. Beverage:almond-milk == Pet:goldfish##1
2. Pet:hamster is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Pet:goldfish is between Pet:hamster and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Pet:goldfish is on the left or right of Pet:hamster##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Pet:ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Pet   | bird | ferret | goldfish        | hamster    |

